Dried zombies are monsters found in the Kharidian Desert and play a small role in the Dealing with Scabaras quest. They are located in area that is affected by desert heat, so bringing water skins is recommended. There is a spring nearby, allowing quick refills therefore, making them a fairly decent training option. A permanent shortcut can be set up by using a rope on an overhanging rock at the westernmost part of the plateau just west of the archaeologists, making the plateau reachable from the Agility Pyramid.
